# Cost: Free forever
#
# Instructions:
#   1. Go to: https://data.cityofnewyork.us/profile/app_tokens
#   2. Click "Create New App Token"
#   3. Fill in: Application Name = "nyc-mcp" (or any name)
#   4. Copy your token
#   5. Paste below (uncomment and replace "your-token-here")
